message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which has been meticulously crafted to provide exceptional value and quality. Given its unique features and benefits, I believe it's worth more than its face value. Considering the cost and effort put into creating this item, I am offering it to you for $125. This price reflects the superior quality and the opportunity to own something truly special. I trust that you will find immense value in it. Thank you for considering my offer.
